<h2>Partnership Request</h2>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p><strong>{{requesting_company_name}}</strong> would like to partner with your company on ServeMax.</p>

{{#if message}}
<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Message:</strong></p>
  <p>{{message}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>By accepting this partnership, you'll be able to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Share jobs with each other</li>
  <li>Collaborate on service coverage</li>
  <li>Expand your service network</li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{respond_url}}" class="button">View Request</a>
</p>

<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;">
  You can accept or decline this partnership request from your Partners page.
</p>
